questionsAndAnswers.question: How would you describe the atmosphere?

answers.answer: Epoch coffee shop has an inviting atmosphere. There is a friendly staff that always try to brighten your day. The customers are mostly laid back. Great place to chill and catch up with friends or meet cool people.

updatesFromCustomers.text: Morning stop at Epoch Coffee - even on weekdays, people find time to work here. Great vibe, lots of folks with laptops. Also checked out the nearby record store, which added to the mood. Good coffee and fresh pastries.
